description:
Arche Eeb Rile Furt was a worker and magic caster of http://anidb.net/ch97463 [Foresight] who volunteered to explore and investigate the http://anidb.net/ch95428 [mysterious tomb]. She was a former noble and student of the Imperial Magic Academy.
Source: Overlord Wiki
name: Arche Eeb Rile Furt
